summary: An Ordinance providing for the dismissal of action No. 75069 in the Superior Court of King County, State of Washington, entitled "In the Matter of the Petition of the City of Seattle to condemn, appropriate and damage private property for the purpose of protecting the supply of fresh water of said city from pollution, as provided for and specified in Ordinance No. 22305 of said city, approved November 3, 1909." as to Page Lumber Company, a corporation, and as the same affects property owned by said Page Lumber Company as set forth in their notice of appearance in said action, more particularly hereinafter described.
